%200%206%200%206-2l-1-2c0-6-10-8-14-4m104%200c-5%206-1%2017%207%2017%205%200%208-4%208-9%200-6-3-10-8-10l-7%202M143%20751c0%203%207%2012%2014%2017%209%206%2010%205%204-5-4-7-18-17-18-12M34%20787c-10%205-8%2019%202%2022%2014%204%2022-14%2010-22-4-2-7-3-12%200m0%202c-4%202-5%207-4%2011%203%2011%2018%2010%2020-2%201-8-9-14-16-9m95%2064c-2%204-1%204%2072%204%2070%200%2071-1%2071-2%200-2-1-3-72-3l-71%201\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          data-srcset=\"/blogs/static/d95693b7a63539ffb568be14e7033d45/f2fbe/622CBE47-A511-4395-B798-8F4F5BB5819C.webp 200w,\n/blogs/static/d95693b7a63539ffb568be14e7033d45/e227a/622CBE47-A511-4395-B798-8F4F5BB5819C.webp 400w,\n/blogs/static/d95693b7a63539ffb568be14e7033d45/0cbce/622CBE47-A511-4395-B798-8F4F5BB5819C.webp 800w,\n/blogs/static/d95693b7a63539ffb568be14e7033d45/92da1/622CBE47-A511-4395-B798-8F4F5BB5819C.webp 1125w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/blogs/static/d95693b7a63539ffb568be14e7033d45/f544b/622CBE47-A511-4395-B798-8F4F5BB5819C.jpg 200w,\n/blogs/static/d95693b7a63539ffb568be14e7033d45/41689/622CBE47-A511-4395-B798-8F4F5BB5819C.jpg 400w,\n/blogs/static/d95693b7a63539ffb568be14e7033d45/a296c/622CBE47-A511-4395-B798-8F4F5BB5819C.jpg 800w,\n/blogs/static/d95693b7a63539ffb568be14e7033d45/c0626/622CBE47-A511-4395-B798-8F4F5BB5819C.jpg 1125w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n          data-src=\"/blogs/static/d95693b7a63539ffb568be14e7033d45/a296c/622CBE47-A511-4395-B798-8F4F5BB5819C.jpg\"\n          alt=\"换个 Pro\"\n          title=\"换个 Pro\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.apple.com/cn/iphone/compare/\">iPhone 对比</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"补充\"><a href=\"#%E8%A1%A5%E5%85%85\" aria-label=\"补充 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>补充</h2>\n<p>最近看了些评测，发现相机的提升实在太强了。首先是夜间模式的能力大幅提升，这个相信大家都已经看过样图和赞美的文章了。</p>\n<p>另外还有几个被广为称赞的细节：\n首先苹果是把三个相机同时打开并实时取景的，在你拍一张照片的时候其实是拍了至少三张不同焦距的照片，并保存下来，你在编辑相片的时候可以随意决定是否切换成其他的焦距。这个可以在相机设置中决定是否关闭</p>\n<p>第二，前置摄像头变成了广角。这意味着和 XS 的相比，脸看上去不会那么大了，Face ID 的能力也肯定会更强。只不过竖屏情况下，苹果通过照片的裁切让拍照的时候不会显得离镜头太远。一旦你这个时候将手机横屏，就能明显地看到整个视角的调整。不过目前看来，这个视角调整的动画还比较生硬</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"对于新 iPhone 的看法","spoiler":"大哥换个肾？","date":"2019/09/20"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/buy-an-iphone11/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/how-to-add/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"如何实现加法和减法","spoiler":"你知道 -1 的补码是多少吗？"}},"next":null}}}